<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 That wonderful magic from the <ORGANIZATION> Disney </ORGANIZATION> animation wand will be in video stores on May 31 in time for summer rentals and sales. <ORGANIZATION> Walt </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Disney </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Home </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Video </ORGANIZATION> is also offering a limited edition <PERSON> Mickey </PERSON> <PERSON> Mouse </PERSON> videocassette to help celebrate <PERSON> Mickey </PERSON>'s 60th birthday. The original feature includes snippets from some of the mouse's greatest hits, including the Socerer's Apprentice segment from `` Fantasia. Other Disney features for summer fun include `` <PERSON> Mickey </PERSON> and the <LOCATION> Beanstalk </LOCATION>,'' `` <PERSON> Donald </PERSON> in Mathmagic Land'' and `` The Reluctant Dragon.'' And hold on to your feathers, duck fans: Disney also plans to release three volumes of the hit TV `` Ducktales'' series, featuring the adventures and misadventures of <PERSON> Duckburg </PERSON>'s leading citizen, <PERSON> Scrooge </PERSON> <PERSON> McDuck </PERSON>, and his nephews <PERSON> Huey </PERSON>, <PERSON> Dewey </PERSON> and <PERSON> Louie </PERSON>. The series has received raves from critics. TV Guide said the animated comedy-adventure show `` features the superior production values and animation kids of all ages have come to expect from <ORGANIZATION> Disney </ORGANIZATION>.'' Also in May HBO is releasing `` Weeds'' and `` House of Games,'' and <ORGANIZATION> Orion </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Home </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Video </ORGANIZATION> has scheduled <PERSON> Danny </PERSON> <PERSON> DeVito </PERSON>'s zany sendup of matricide, `` Throw Mama From the Train.'' Videos reviewed this week: `` Weeds'' -LRB- <ORGANIZATION> HBO </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Video </ORGANIZATION>, VHS @ Beta, $ 89.99, Rated R
